# lemoineTriangle

- _lemoineTriangle(t)_

Answer the Lemoine triangle of the triangle _t_.

~~~spl svg=A
let t = Triangle([0 0; 5 0; 2 3]);
[
	t,
	t.lemoineTriangle
].GeometryCollection
~~~

